RATIONALE: Cryosurgery kills cancer cells by freezing them.

 Cryosurgery followed by lumpectomy or mastectomy may be an effective treatment for breast lesions.

 PURPOSE: Phase I trial to study the effectiveness of cryosurgery in treating women who have breast lesions.

